  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered customer support agent that answers questions from your content",
    "Human escalation with seamless handoff to live agents",
    "Conversation insights: feedback, bugs, feature requests surfaced automatically",
    "Integrations with Zendesk, Intercom, Freshdesk, HubSpot, Gorgias, Slack, Teams",
